text: Cindy is a fantastic radiographer—patient, friendly, and reassuring. She made my MRI experience comfortable and stress-free.

Cindy is an outstanding radiographer—patient, friendly, and reassuring. She made me feel completely at ease during my MRI, ensuring a smooth and comfortable experience. Her professionalism and warmth gave me confidence that everything would be fine.

Went here for physiotherapy session with parkway. The service at the counter was very professional and good. Therapist was very nice and patient towards my conditions as well. Totally recommend the service here. Very empathetic and I really needed that for my injury condition. Thank you.

This place has mostly medical centers. hard to visit if you don't drive as there's no nearby train stations. A few eateries (very few though), wheelchair accessible. Every floor has a toilet, which is very clean.

I'm so fortunate to work in camden Medical Centre and met with good and resourceful security officer Mr Fazly. I left my key card to go to the ladies. Everyone has left the office. My bag, phone was in the office. Frantically, I seek help from Mr Fazly and due to his professionalism and tactfullness...from contacting the management office, communication with the emergency contact person of my company, the wait and all...I managed to get to my colleague, open the door, and got back my bag and phone. I'm so proud to have a security officer in my office building who is so humble, honest, sincere, helpful and tact. Thumbs up Camden Management and it's Security Team especially MR FAZLY.
